        <maml:title>-------------------------- Example 1 --------------------------</maml:title>
        <dev:code>PS C:\&gt; $SecurePassword = Read-Host -Prompt 'Enter password' -AsSecureString
Enter password: ***********
PS C:\&gt; ConvertTo-PlainString -SecureString $SecurePassword
password123</dev:code>
        <dev:remarks>
          <maml:para>The above example prompts the user to enter a password using Read-Host with the AsSecureString parameter which will return a secure string encrypting the password. Then, ConvertTo-PlainString converts the secured password back to a unencrypted string.</maml:para>
